'''維托沙大道'''（{{lang-bg|булевард "Витоша"}}）是[[保加利亞|保加利亞]]首都[[索菲亞|索菲亞]]的主要商業街，沿線聚集了眾多商店、餐廳和酒吧。維托沙大道的名稱來自於索菲亞附近的[[維托沙山|維托沙山]]。2007年，按照[[高緯環球|高緯環球]]的研究，維托沙大道是世界第22昂貴的商業街<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cushwakeasia.com/aboutus/pdf/news/gcpre2005.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2006-09-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061005234357/http://www.cushwakeasia.com/aboutus/pdf/news/gcpre2005.pdf |archivedate=2006-10-05 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.europe-re.com/system/main.php?pageid=1393&articleid=5903&objectid=10019|title=Europe Real Estate - News and publications about commercial real estate|publisher=|accessdate=2016-02-29|archive-date=2012-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120205205732/http://www.europe-re.com/system/main.php?pageid=1393&articleid=5903&objectid=10019|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.segabg.com/online/article.asp?issueid=283&sectionid=1&id=00003|title=СЕГА -|author=снимка: Борислав Николов|work=SEGA Online|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070311073136/http://www.segabg.com/online/article.asp?issueid=283&sectionid=1&id=00003|archivedate=2007-03-11}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dnes.bg/article.php?cat=1&id=15108|title="Витошка" е 22-та най-скъпа търговска улица в света|date=2005-10-28|publisher=|accessdate=2016-02-29|archive-date=2007-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070928093725/http://www.dnes.bg/article.php?cat=1&id=15108|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2007年，索菲亞公佈了一個維托沙大道的改建計劃，計劃將這條路恢復與1930年代的風格<ref>{{cite web |url=http://trud.bg/Default.asp?statid=46254&rubr=0&izd=2&fsize=&swidth=800&tr=1&im=05&id=19&iy=2007 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2007-05-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927191343/http://trud.bg/Default.asp?statid=46254&rubr=0&izd=2&fsize=&swidth=800&tr=1&im=05&id=19&iy=2007 |archivedate=2007-09-27 }}</ref>。

